    "body": "This PR adds the separate code path for the fp8 kernel with transpose of V in the producer warpgroup, with all tests given in the script passing. There's a lot of duplication of code that we might want to address before merging into main. Also, I haven't added the max offset subtraction yet (by 8.0f) -- I need to track down a specific performance regression with hdim 128 causal before I add this.\r\n\r\n[fp8_new_times_after_rebase_072624.log](https://github.com/user-attachments/files/16388793/fp8_new_times_after_rebase_072624.log)\r\n",
